title: Earth's Geological Processes
description: An illustration depicting various geological processes on Earth. The image shows a cross-section of the Earth, featuring a sun in the sky, clouds, and rain falling over a landscape that includes mountains, forests, and a body of water. On the right side, volcanic activity is illustrated with lava flowing from a volcano, while the left side shows icebergs in the water, indicating a diverse range of geological features and processes.

title: Earth from Space
description: A detailed depiction of Earth as seen from space, showcasing continents, oceans, and cloud formations. The image highlights Europe, Africa, and parts of Asia, with vibrant colors representing land and water.
